descriptionHtml:
One more conan save for skyrim!:DD
Conan lvl1 in the Riverwood. Don\'t have the fathers sword but you should craft it for him. He\'s wearing own armor as seen screens. Once again if someone can could do an follower from him.
Sharpshooters ENB used in screens.

Mods you need to get the look:
	
High Res Face Maps for Men by Geonox:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4141
	
ApachiiSkyHair: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168

BFG - Better FaceGen:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6953 (not sure if needed)

Flans Eyes for Skyrim:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14539 (optional, may use different blue eyes also)

Also optional 	
Better males: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2488

Recommended armor & sword.

CONAN THE BARBARIAN outfits:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4793

Conan Swords:http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4217

Let me know if i miss something:P
